Title: Tool calling LLM
User->LLM Client: User initiates a query
Note over LLM Client: Client adds system messages\nand tool calling instructions
LLM Client->LLM Model: formatted prompt
Note over LLM Model: LLM processes the prompt and\nidentifies if a tool is needed
LLM Model->LLM Client: return tool call instructions
LLM Client->Tool: Call tool with parameters
Tool->LLM Client: return tool results
Note over LLM Client: Client adds system messages\nand results to the prompt
LLM Client->LLM Model: formatted prompt with tool results
LLM Model->LLM Client: return generated response
LLM Client->User: return generated response